{"title":"Set the alarm for 0:00","description":"Turn on the alarm clock on 0:00 with sound. midnight alarm clock. Free and simple alarm online. Set alarm for midnight.","content":"Is there a need to set an alarm for midnight? Use our simple and free alarm clock online! \nSet the alarm for midnight or choose another time by setting it yourself or by selecting from the list. An alarm clock with a sound that you can set yourself. After setting the time, press the **Add** button to turn on the alarm.\n\nTurn on the alarm clock for midnight and go about your business, the alarm clock will definitely notify you at exactly 0:00.\n\nAll alarms are saved in your browser, so you can reuse them. The clock beautifully shows the time remaining from midnight, with an accuracy of seconds and milliseconds."}